# Fincz-Track Notification Service API Tests
# Author: Kaunain Ahmad
# Created: April 2026

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### Health Check (No Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/test

### Send Notification (Requires Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "toEmail": "user@example.com",
  "subject": "Test Notification",
  "message": "This is a test notification from Fincz-Track"
}

### Get User Notifications (Requires Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Trigger Tax Reminder Check (Requires Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/tax-reminder
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Trigger Portfolio Alert Check (Requires Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/portfolio-alert
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}